and every fourth year after that, a second or third class city or a town
may by ordinance establish or abolish a city or town court. An
ordinance to establish a city or town court must be adopted not less
than one (1) year before the judge's term would begin under
IC 3-10-5.5-4 or section 3 of this chapter.
